       then A23:    eps^2 <= b/2 by A17,AXIOMS:22;
A24:    a = z^2 + b;
A25:    (z + eps)^2 = z^2 + 2*z*eps + eps^2 by Th63
        .= z^2 + (2*z*eps + eps^2);
